44
00:03:42,965 --> 00:03:48,801
Criminals. That's what
you are: criminals.

45
00:03:49,605 --> 00:03:53,120
Assassins!
Damned assassins!

46
00:04:10,485 --> 00:04:14,797
Murderous hogs. Murderous hogs!

47
00:04:15,845 --> 00:04:17,284
Hogs!

48
00:04:17,285 --> 00:04:20,721
