194
00:19:21,005 --> 00:19:23,394
The restocking!

195
00:19:33,325 --> 00:19:35,281
Comrades!

196
00:19:35,445 --> 00:19:40,285
Laugh! Today
everything can change!

197
00:19:40,286 --> 00:19:42,241
Baroni!

198
00:19:45,205 --> 00:19:47,719
Make him eat it,
today is carnival!

199
00:19:48,525 --> 00:19:50,084
"Milk and wine, subtle poison".

200
