Did you see if he was happy?

240
00:23:00,635 --> 00:23:03,800
- Not, really...
- You are a fool, you are blind!

241
00:23:04,765 --> 00:23:10,442
Poor Olmo had to leave
the house and his daughter.

242
00:23:10,885 --> 00:23:13,035
